title: Energy Minister says Octane 95 available from tomorrow
body_lines: Power and Energy Minister Kanchana Wijesekera said that Octane 95 petrol will be supplied to filling stations islandwide from today.
"With the unloading fuel from two cargo freighters Octane 95 petrol will be available for the next six weeks quite comfortably," the minister said.
He requested Octane 95 users not to stay in lines for 92 Petrol and to obtain 95 Petrol from tomorrow.(DSB)
